00:22:53,600 --> 00:22:54,460
remember this.

291
00:22:54,840 --> 00:22:57,100
Liberation Road, Section 6, Number 178.

292
00:22:57,160 --> 00:22:58,890
That's Duan Zhigang's winery.

293
00:22:59,040 --> 00:23:01,240
There's a safe in the cabinet in the living room.

294
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:02,600
The password is 3160.

295
00:23:03,440 --> 00:23:04,300
What's inside?

296
00:23:04,720 --> 00:23:05,680
In 1994,

297
00:23:06,080 --> 00:23:10,810
a tape recording of Xu Chengliang and the other two coordinating their testimonies.

298
00:23:14,360 --> 00:23:14,960
Okay.

299
00:23:15,960 --> 00:23:16,640
I got it.

300
00:24:23,960 --> 00:24:25,480
Hey, Lingling.

301
00:24:30,400 --> 00:24:30,930
Alright.

302
00:24:31,320 --> 00:24:32,120
I understand.

303
00:25:05,480 --> 00:25:06,360
Come tell me

304
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:08,410
what's happening tonight.

305
00:25:09,760 --> 00:25:10,680
Say something.

306
00:25:11,640 --> 00:25:13,720
I'm talking to you.

307
00:25:16,080 --> 00:25:17,680
As long as my brother is alive,

308
00:25:17,680 --> 00:25:20,010
I know why I have to endure this suffering.

309
00:25:20,800 --> 00:25:21,800
He hates me.

310
00:25:22,120 --> 00:25:23,680
He insists on letting this disease

311
00:25:23,680 --> 00:25:25,480
torture him for a few more years.

312
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:27,040
He hates me.

313
00:25:28,400 --> 00:25:29,440
For him,

314
00:25:31,160 --> 00:25:32,520
I gave up my own life.

315
00:25:35,080 --> 00:25:36,740
That's just how my brother is.

316
00:25:37,160 --> 00:25:38,880
He has never asked

317
00:25:39,240 --> 00:25:40,640
me to do anything for him.

318
00:25:41,400 --> 00:25:42,280
Not even once.

319
00:28:03,960 --> 00:28:04,440
Boss.

320
00:28:04,560 --> 00:28:06,360
We've searched everywhere around the warehouse.

321
00:28:06,360 --> 00:28:07,600
Still nothing.

322
00:28:08,160 --> 00:28:10,080
Should we expand the search area?

323
00:28:13,400 --> 00:28:14,060
Captain Li.

324
00:28:14,880 --> 00:28:16,400
In the Qinglong River, 1.5 kilometers away,

325
00:28:16,400 --> 00:28:17,560
