326
00:28:17,560 --> 00:28:18,880
There was an axe wrapped inside.

327
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:19,880
I measured it briefly.

328
00:28:19,880 --> 00:28:21,520
It matches the murder weapon's size.

329
00:28:21,520 --> 00:28:22,360
Get it to forensics immediately.

330
00:28:22,360 --> 00:28:22,920
Got it.

331
00:28:49,360 --> 00:28:50,000
Hao,

332
00:28:50,960 --> 00:28:52,760
