333
00:28:53,320 --> 00:28:54,320
Where are you now?

334
00:28:54,680 --> 00:28:55,680
Guangming Alley.

335
00:28:56,760 --> 00:28:57,600
Master,

336
00:28:57,600 --> 00:28:59,000
