338
00:29:00,520 --> 00:29:01,240
Listen to me.

339
00:29:01,240 --> 00:29:02,520
Don't be reckless.

340
00:29:02,640 --> 00:29:03,520
Don't follow too closely.

341
00:29:03,520 --> 00:29:05,050
I'm heading back right now.

342
00:29:06,360 --> 00:29:06,760
