372
00:37:16,480 --> 00:37:18,840
I'll pin everything on him.

373
00:37:36,320 --> 00:37:36,920
Zhao Lun.

374
00:37:45,080 --> 00:37:45,480
Hello.

375
00:37:45,840 --> 00:37:46,440
Lingling,

376
00:37:46,880 --> 00:37:48,140
