379
00:37:53,040 --> 00:37:54,320
I got one tape.

380
00:37:54,920 --> 00:37:57,000
You should get out now.

381
00:37:58,120 --> 00:37:58,720
Hurry up.

382
00:37:59,120 --> 00:38:01,520
Get the tape to the police immediately.

383
00:38:02,160 --> 00:38:03,720
As long as Xu Chengliang gets arrested,

384
00:38:03,720 --> 00:38:05,520
